1122
01:23:08,645 --> 01:23:12,158
Target in sight!
Where in hell is Major Kong?

1123
01:23:34,950 --> 01:23:36,159
What about Major Kong?

1124
01:24:03,206 --> 01:24:06,752
Mr. President, I would not
rule out the chance...

1125
01:24:06,822 --> 01:24:09,756
to preserve a nucleus
of human specimens.

1126
01:24:09,830 --> 01:24:12,614
It would be quite easy...

1127
01:24:14,919 --> 01:24:19,808
at the bottom of some
of our deeper mine shafts.

1128
01:24:19,880 --> 01:24:24,517
The radioactivity would never penetrate
a mine some thousands of feet deep.

1129
01:24:24,584 --> 01:24:28,674
And in a matter of weeks, sufficient
improvements in dwelling space...

1130
01:24:28,743 --> 01:24:30,597
could easily be provided.

1131
01:24:30,663 --> 01:24:33,314
How long would you have
to stay down there?

1132
01:24:33,383 --> 01:24:37,092
Well, that's, you know...

1133
01:24:37,161 --> 01:24:39,714
Cobalt thorium G.

1134
01:24:49,545 --> 01:24:53,223
Radioactive half-life of...

1135
01:24:55,209 --> 01:24:59,748
I would think that possibly
one hundred years.

1136
01:25:01,991 --> 01:25:05,822
You mean, people could actually
stay down there for 100 years?

1137
01:25:05,897 --> 01:25:08,035
It would not be difficult,
Mein Fuhrer.

1138
01:25:08,105 --> 01:25:10,243
Nuclear reactors could...

1139
01:25:10,313 --> 01:25:12,582
I'm sorry, Mr. President.

1140
01:25:12,650 --> 01:25:16,294
Nuclear reactors could provide
power almost indefinitely.

1141
01:25:16,362 --> 01:25:19,079
Greenhouses could maintain
plant life.

1142
01:25:19,147 --> 01:25:22,592
Animals could be bred
and slaughtered.

1143
01:25:22,664 --> 01:25:26,920
A quick survey would have to be made of
the available mine sites in the country.

1144
01:25:26,986 --> 01:25:30,631
But I would guess
that a dwelling space...

1145
01:25:30,698 --> 01:25:34,211
for several hundred thousand of
our people could easily be provided.

1146
01:25:34,282 --> 01:25:37,282
Well, I would hate
to have to decide...

1147
01:25:37,354 --> 01:25:40,137
who stays up and who goes down.

1148
01:25:40,203 --> 01:25:43,946
Well, that would not be
necessary, Mr. President.

1149
01:25:44,012 --> 01:25:46,762
It could easily be accomplished
with a computer.

1150
01:25:46,828 --> 01:25:49,030
And the computer could
be set and programmed...

1151
01:25:49,098 --> 01:25:52,033
to accept factors
from youth, health...

1152
01:25:52,105 --> 01:25:55,139
sexual fertility, intelligence...

1153
01:25:55,210 --> 01:25:57,600
and a cross-section
of necessary skills.

1154
01:25:57,674 --> 01:25:59,846
Of course, it would be
absolutely vital...

1155
01:25:59,915 --> 01:26:03,712
that our top government
and military men be included...

1156
01:26:03,787 --> 01:26:08,425
to foster and impart the required
principles of leadership and tradition.

1157
01:26:14,221 --> 01:26:17,034
Naturally, they would breed
prodigiously.

1158
01:26:17,099 --> 01:26:19,783
There would be much time
and little to do.

1159
01:26:21,323 --> 01:26:26,058
But with the proper breeding techniques
and a ratio of, say...

1160
01:26:26,124 --> 01:26:28,775
ten females to each male...

1161
01:26:28,844 --> 01:26:33,284
they could then work their way back
to the present gross national product...

1162
01:26:33,356 --> 01:26:35,048
within 20 years.

1163
01:26:36,205 --> 01:26:38,825
But look, Doctor.
Wouldn't this nucleus of survivors...

1164
01:26:38,895 --> 01:26:43,780
be so grief-stricken
and anguished that they...

1165
01:26:43,851 --> 01:26:47,201
well, envy the dead
and not want to go on living?

1166
01:26:47,277 --> 01:26:49,994
No, sir. Excuse me.

1167
01:26:58,894 --> 01:27:02,669
When they go down into the mine,
everyone would still be alive.

1168
01:27:02,734 --> 01:27:04,742
There would be
no shocking memories...

1169
01:27:04,815 --> 01:27:09,286
and the prevailing emotion will be one
of nostalgia for those left behind...

1170
01:27:09,357 --> 01:27:12,108
combined with a spirit of...

1171
01:27:12,173 --> 01:27:14,508
bold curiosity for
the adventure ahead!

1172
01:27:31,311 --> 01:27:33,167
Doctor...

1173
01:27:35,278 --> 01:27:40,495
you mentioned the ratio
of ten women to each man.

1174
01:27:40,558 --> 01:27:43,558
Now, wouldn't that
necessitate the abandonment...

1175
01:27:43,630 --> 01:27:47,276
of the so-called
monogamous sexual relationship?

1176
01:27:47,344 --> 01:27:50,824
I mean, as far as men were concerned?

1177
01:27:50,896 --> 01:27:52,205
Regrettably, yes.

1178
01:27:52,272 --> 01:27:57,422
But it is a sacrifice required
for the future of the human race.

1179
01:27:57,489 --> 01:28:02,276
I hasten to add that since each man
will be required to do prodigious...

1180
01:28:03,983 --> 01:28:05,839
service along these lines...

1181
01:28:05,904 --> 01:28:09,549
the women will have to be selected
for their sexual characteristics...

1182
01:28:09,617 --> 01:28:13,228
which will have to be of
a highly stimulating nature.

1183
01:28:13,296 --> 01:28:16,974
I must confess, you have an
astonishingly good idea there, Doctor.

1184
01:28:18,097 --> 01:28:19,471
Thank you, sir.

1185
01:28:19,537 --> 01:28:22,385
We ought to look at this
from the military point of view.

1186
01:28:22,449 --> 01:28:26,225
I mean,
supposing the Ruskies...

1187
01:28:26,289 --> 01:28:29,102
stashed away some big bombs,
see, and we didn't?

1188
01:28:29,168 --> 01:28:31,951
When they come out in 100 years,
they could take over!

1189
01:28:32,016 --> 01:28:33,708
I agree, Mr. President.

1190
01:28:33,777 --> 01:28:37,225
They might try a sneak attack so they
could take over our mine shaft space.

1191
01:28:37,297 --> 01:28:41,737
It'd be extremely naive of us to
imagine that these new developments...

1192
01:28:41,809 --> 01:28:44,624
are gonna cause any change
in Soviet expansionist policy!

1193
01:28:44,689 --> 01:28:47,408
I mean, we must be
increasingly on the alert...

1194
01:28:47,475 --> 01:28:49,896
to prevent them from taking over
other mine shaft space...

1195
01:28:49,970 --> 01:28:51,825
in order to breed more
prodigiously than we do...

1196
01:28:51,889 --> 01:28:54,888
thus knocking us out through
superior numbers when we emerge!

1197
01:28:54,961 --> 01:28:58,890
Mr. President, we must not allow
a mineshaft gap!

1198
01:28:58,961 --> 01:29:00,968
Sir!

1199
01:29:01,041 --> 01:29:03,213
I have a plan...

1200
01:29:04,689 --> 01:29:06,927
Mein Fuhrer...

1201
01:29:06,994 --> 01:29:09,482
I can walk!

